dc_description_s: This data represents trauma center sites for Wisconsin in 2021. [This dataset contains locations and attributes of trauma centers licensed by the state of Wisconsin. The data is used for planning, management and analysis by Wisconsin Department of Health Services staff and by other government agencies. For more information please visit the Wisconsin Department of Health Services website: https://www.dhs.wisconsin.gov/trauma/index.htm]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For access to the most current data available, please visit: https://data.dhsgis.wi.gov/datasets/595fd0136ac546afbd68be5cd544732f_12?geometry=-103.911%2C41.861%2C-76.160%2C47.331
